---
import BaseLayout from '../layouts/BaseLayout.astro';
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Macro Monk | Macro and Training Tracker"
  description="Track macros, training, and body composition without fake scarcity or ad-heavy upsells."
  lang="en"
  switchToEn="/"
  switchToFi="/fi/"
  homeUrl="/"
  blogUrl="/blog/"
>
  <section class="hero">
    <div class="hero-copy">
      <p class="eyebrow">For lifters and athletes</p>
      <h1>Track macros and training without getting sold every 30 seconds.</h1>
      <p class="hero-catchphrase">
        Macro Monk stays clean: practical logging, serious tracking, and no manipulative funnel patterns.
      </p>
      <p class="lede">
        Most trackers pretend to be free, then choke your setup with tiny limits, ads, and endless
        upsells. Macro Monk is built for people who actually want results.
      </p>
      <div class="hero-actions">
        <a class="button primary" href="https://app.macromonk.fi/" target="_blank" rel="noreferrer">
          Start tracking
        </a>
        <a class="button ghost" href="/blog/">Read blog</a>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="hero-visual">
      <div class="logo-frame">
        <img src="/macro-monk-favicon.png" alt="Macro Monk emblem" />
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="difference">
    <h2>See the difference</h2>
    <ol class="difference-steps">
      <li>Set calories and macros, then pick your phase: Cut, Bulk, or Maintain.</li>
      <li>Log meals and train like normal.</li>
      <li>Track what is left for the day with clear numbers and less friction.</li>
    </ol>
    <p class="difference-note">
      Build your own food database and avoid low-quality crowdsourced entries. No fake item caps, no forced
      Pro walls.
    </p>
  </section>

  <section class="pricing">
    <h2>Simple pricing</h2>
    <p class="pricing-intro">No hidden layers. Gift cards available at the same amounts.</p>
    <div class="pricing-grid">
      <article class="price-card">
        <p class="plan-name">30 days</p>
        <p class="plan-price">10 EUR</p>
      </article>
      <article class="price-card">
        <p class="plan-name">365 days</p>
        <p class="plan-price">99 EUR</p>
      </article>
      <article class="price-card">
        <p class="plan-name">Trial</p>
        <p class="plan-price">7 days free</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>

  <section class="feature-guide">
    <h2>Features built for real progress</h2>
    <div class="feature-grid">
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Daily dashboard with coaching</h3>
        <p>Sleep, readiness, stress, soreness, and load in one clear daily recommendation.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Body composition trend tracking</h3>
        <p>Running 7-day averages and weekly trend changes to reduce noisy scale decisions.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Phase intelligence</h3>
        <p>Cut, bulk, and maintenance check-ins with practical macro adjustments.</p>
      </article>
      <article class="feature-card">
        <h3>Fast meal logging</h3>
        <p>Reusable meals, fast edits, and your own personal food data for better accuracy.</p>
      </article>
    </div>
  </section>
</BaseLayout>
